---
/* Programme Section — Bento grid, editorial header | Light Editorial */
---

<section id="programme" class="bg-surface py-[var(--spacing-section-gap)]">
  <div class="container-main">

    <!-- Asymmetric header -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-8">
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display font-bold tracking-tighter text-on-surface reveal">CURRICULUM<br /><span class="text-outline-variant">AUGMENTÉ</span></h2>
      <div class="max-w-md text-right font-body text-on-surface-variant text-sm border-r-4 border-primary pr-6 reveal delay-1">
        En 12 semaines, nous reconstruirons ton arsenal technique et stratégique pour devenir l'expert indispensable.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bento grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

      <!-- Card 1: Architecture IA (2 cols) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-surface-container-low p-10 relative overflow-hidden group border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg reveal delay-1">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 font-sans text-outline-variant text-6xl font-black opacity-10">01</div>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-6 text-4xl block">psychology</span>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-tighter text-on-surface">Intelligence IA</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed max-w-lg mb-8">
          <strong>Prompting avancé</strong>, <strong>agents IA</strong>, intégration dans tes workflows d'automatisation. Multiplie ta productivité par 10.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="chip">Prompting</span>
          <span class="chip">Agents IA</span>
          <span class="chip">RAG Systems</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Maîtrise Make (1 col) -->
      <div class="bg-white p-10 flex flex-col justify-between border-t-4 border-primary shadow-sm border-x border-b border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg reveal delay-2">
        <div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mb-6 block text-3xl">account_tree</span>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-tighter text-on-surface">Maîtrise de Make</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            Scénarios d'automatisation de A à Z. <strong>APIs</strong>, <strong>webhooks</strong>, architecture avancée.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-outline-variant/20 font-sans text-[10px] text-primary tracking-widest font-bold uppercase">Make Partner Level 5</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Puissance n8n (1 col) -->
      <div class="bg-white p-10 border-b-4 border-tertiary shadow-sm border-x border-t border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg reveal delay-3">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary mb-6 block text-3xl">device_hub</span>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-tighter text-on-surface">Puissance n8n</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          Workflows <strong>open-source</strong>, <strong>auto-hébergés</strong>, sans limites. Déploie des automatisations que tu possèdes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4: Terminal des Projets (2 cols) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-surface-bright p-10 relative overflow-hidden group border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg reveal delay-4">
        <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20rem] text-on-surface">deployed_code</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-6 uppercase tracking-tighter text-on-surface">Branding & Business</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <div class="font-sans text-primary text-xs mb-2 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Branding & Offre</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant"><strong>Positionnement</strong>, <strong>pricing premium</strong>, personal branding qui attire les bons clients.</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-sans text-primary text-xs mb-2 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Communauté</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Réseau de <strong>freelances augmentés</strong>, accountability, partage de deals et opportunités.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
